# **DRAFT VERY ROUGH** Set up dnsmasq to serve dhcp and internal dns

YOU ARE HERE.

```sh
git archive --remote=git@bitbucket.org:suspectdevicesadmin/susdev-dns.git --format=tar HEAD |tar -xvf - -O hosts/admin.hosts>/etc/hosts
x hosts/admin.hosts
```

